data.description: Charming & updated home on wooded lot with fenced yard. Three bedrooms in main level, included master suite with walk-in closet and updated bathroom. Second floor includes  a large bonus room plus a very spacious second master suite with walk -in closets and a room for storage or small private office.  The whole upstairs is an ideal space for private in-law's or extended family. Refinished hardwood floors, new carpets and paint. New quartz kitchen counter tops. Great room with cathedral ceilings and fireplace. Enclosed porch/sunroom overlooking the wooded back yard. Lovely front porch surrounded by beautiful greenery in peaceful cul de sac street.
